Overview

[Exo 31:1](../../../bib/kjv/exo031.htm#001.md), Bezaleel and Aholiab are
appointed and qualified for the work of the tabernacle; [Exo
31:12](../../../bib/kjv/exo031.htm#012.md), The observation of the sabbath
is again commanded; [Exo 31:18](../../../bib/kjv/exo031.htm#018.md), Moses
receives the two tables.

